          <h4 class="card--">We will contact you to finalize details.</h4>
          <p class="">Each entrepreneur has a limited availability and they will do their best to accommodate requested dates in their schedule.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
      <!-- insert <div class="card"> -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="">
          <h2 class="">Enjoy & Learn</h2>
          <h4 class="">Finally, pay online and enjoy your meal.</h4>
          <p class="">Once details are confirmed, you’ll receive a confirmation email with all details needed before arriving at the dinner spot.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="btn btn-danger btn-block" src=<%= link_to "Book a seat", root_path %></a>
</div>

